y activity and wear sunglasses when outdoors.<\/p>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>Eyelid Aesthetics (Blepharoplasty) Eyelid surgery (blepharoplasty) is a surgical procedure to change the shape and\/or size of the eyelids. It can be performed on the upper and\/or lower eyelids. Excess skin on the upper eyelid can cause the eyelid to sag and the eyes to look tired. Excess fat in the lower eyelid can create [&hellip;]<\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":1,"featured_media":516,"comment_status":"open","ping_status":"open","sticky":false,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":{"footnotes":""},"categories":[1,14],"tags":[],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/burakerdur.com\/en\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/515"}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/burakerdur.com\/en\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/burakerdur.com\/en\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/post"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/burakerdur.com\/en\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/users\/1"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/burakerdur.com\/en\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/comments?post=515"}],"version-history":[{"count":2,"href":"https:\/\/burakerdur.com\/en\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/515\/revisions"}],"predecessor-version":[{"id":630,"href":"https:\/\/burakerdur.com\/en\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/515\/revisions\/630"}],"wp:featuredmedia":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/burakerdur.com\/en\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media\/516"}],"wp:attachment":[{"href":"https:\/\/burakerdur.com\/en\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media?parent=515"}],"wp:term":[{"taxonomy":"category","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/burakerdur.com\/en\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/categories?post=515"},{"taxonomy":"post_tag","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/burakerdur.com\/en\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/tags?post=515"}],"curies":[{"name":"wp","href":"https:\/\/api.w.org\/{rel}","templated":true}]}}